Statue of Liberty Fallen! – Prophecy | Maurice Sklar at The Prophecy Club Radio (1 of 3)
Stan Johnson and Maurice Sklar discuss the vision from God to Maurice about the future of America. He saw a dream, where Angel smashed Statue of Liberty into pieces. As a result, powerful earthquake occurred, California, East and West coasts fell into the ocean, America split right in the middle in two parts. Three EMP bombs go off high in the ...

There is a sister in Christ, Kora, who said she got a word from the Lord Jesus, "March 20, It will begin" and the number 1414 with it. She didn't know what the number 1414 meant.. A few days later I was reading my Bible and JESUS led me to see page 1414 is the page the dragon is hurled to earth and goes after the Saints, and the beast rises out of the sea(Revelation 12, 13:1). It is a very dark period of time before JESUS returns to destroy His enemies, and restore all things new.


If you do not know JESUS, He is GOD the SON, and He loves you so much. There is a heaven, and a hell. JESUS said, "I am the way, the truth, and the life, no one comes to GOD except through me". Hell is a horrible place, and will be everlasting torment for everyone who chooses to go there. It was created for the fallen angels who left heaven to deceive humans. They deceived man into rebelling against GOD. And again, in this final period of time, they will try to deceive us into believing we can be GOD, that we are in control of our destiny. They will try to convince you that connecting yourself to electronics will make you more powerful, further evolved. But in doing so will enslave you even further to there sinister plan of sealing your destiny to hell. They don't want you to give control to JESUS, they want to control you with an electronic device that can send there signals to your brain(RFID). They want you on there frequency, not on GOD's. They want you permanently connected to them and permanently disconnected from the Saviour of your soul. Think aliens = fallen angels...
I don't know if you have a relationship with GOD through His SON JESUS, if you don't.. GOD sent His SON JESUS to be the sacrifice that would pay for our crimes(sin) against Him. Death is the penalty for sin, sin is the reason we die, and is what separated us from GOD in the first place. GOD the SON had to become a man, live a perfect life without sin(obedient to commandments), die your death on the cross so that He could pardon you. He literally judged your wrongs, your sins(rebelliousness), on His own body so that He could legally pardon you. He did it because of His awesome love for you, so He could forgive you of every wrong you have ever done and ever will do in your life on earth. When judgment day comes, you have nothing to fear, your sins are cleared, thanks to the BLOOD of JESUS shed on the cross for you. Don't waste another day, you may not have another day...
For GOD so loved the world that He gave His only begotten SON JESUS, that whoever believes in Him shall not perish but have everlasting life. For GOD sent not His SON into the world to condemn it, but that the world through Him might be saved(John 3:16-17). And everyone who calls on the name of the Lord Jesus will be saved(Acts 2:21)...
P.S. Know where you would go if you had to get to higher ground quickly. Think about what you would take if you had to emergency evacuate..? And most important of all, know the will of God for you and He will show you what to do..
